[categories_description] => stdClass Object
(
[1] =>

Choosing your label material



  • Choose the shape you want from the grid below

  • Click on the picture of the label size you want

  • Click on the label colour of your choice

  • Choose the size pack you want

  • Choose how many packs you want

  • Go to the checkout by clicking the 'Add to Cart' button

severity:
White Opaque (for blockout) paper labels - Gloss only.

Has a higher level of white pigment to provide an enhanced level of opacity. Ideal for when you need to block out printing or text underneath the label.

White FR8 for frozen products - Gloss only.

Developed especially to meet the severe requirements of labelling goods in cold-store conditions
timestamp: FR8 is a true freezer label. Excellent adhesion to cardboard and polyethylene. Designed to stick to goods that are frozen already. Just wipe of the frost and stick the label to the frozen product. Matt & gloss.

severity:
White WLK 202 for wine bottle labels - Gloss only.

Designed by the wine industry specifically to go on to wine bottles. Enhanced adhesive and water resistance. Tested and proven on surfaces affected by condensation
timestamp: dry and recycled bottles. Labels will not slip or move after application. WLK 202 gives excellent ice bucket performance
ip_address: so they can be dunked in an ice bucket without disintegrating.

severity:
Gold Foil - Matt & Gloss.

Metallic foil labels that are ideal for presentation certificates and other decorative presentations.

Suitable Printers

Offset and screen print.
Laser & photocopier may work but the printing can scratch off easily. Not recommended or guaranteed.

Silver Foil - Matt & Gloss.

Metallic foil labels that are ideal for presentation certificates and other decorative presentations.

Suitable Printers

Offset and screen print.
Laser & photocopier may work but the printing can scratch off easily. Not recommended or guaranteed.

Shimmer Gold - Matt only.

Make your labels sparkle with all new shimmer gold. These labels are very unique and will make your product stand out.

Shimmer Silver - Matt only.

Make your labels sparkle with all new shimmer gold. These labels are very unique and will make your product stand out.

Uncoated Ivory Wine Labels - Matt only.

Ivory colour with a textured finish. Classy look on your wine bottles!

Suitable Printers

Laser and offset.
Uncoated Ivory can be printed with an inkjet
timestamp: but if the label gets wet the ink will run. This is significant especially for white wines which are often cooled in an ice bucket.

severity:
Car Tyre Stock - Matt only.

Car Tyre Stock has a very aggressive adhesive. Should be used only where you need a label material that needs to stay stuck permanently. Once it is properly applied it won't come off.

Suitable Printers

Not recommended for printing.
Best used for hand written information. It can be offset printed but the labels can peel off and stick to the machine
timestamp: which are very difficult to remove. Not recommended or guaranteed.
